data.description: This 3 bed, 1 bath updated farmhouse is located in the heart of Waitsburg's historic district. The spacious remodeled kitchen boasts gorgeous granite countertops, breakfast bar, and newer stainless steel appliances. Off the kitchen you'll find a cozy living room with tall ceilings, gorgeous hardwood floors, and lots of natural light; making it a delightful spot for your morning coffee. Updated spa bath, new ductless system in primary, and new electrical. Spacious .28 acre lot with charming front porch, fruit trees, and shop with 50 amp RV hookup. Entertain friends outdoors & fire up the grill for a backyard BBQ. Located just blocks from downtown Waitsburg...you'll be steps from shops, restaurants & the park!
